subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Roger Federer rallied from two sets down to defeat the 29th-seeded Julien Benneteau in the third round. Novak Djokovic, Maria Sharapova and Kim Clijsters were among the other winners Friday.
